Example of a full URI with host name and port number for a key: o3://omhostname:9862/vol1/bucket1/key1 With a service id for a volume: o3://omserviceid/vol1/ Short URI should start from the volume. Example of a short URI for a bucket: vol1/bucket1 Any unspecified information will be identified from the config files.
